the series includes the splendid , idle forties ( 1902 ) ; the conqueror ( 1902 ) , which is a fictionalized biography of alexander hamilton ; and her sensational , semi - autobiographical novel black oxen ( 1923 ) , about an aging woman who miraculously becomes young again after glandular therapy .

